Remove duplicate src/supermodel/tsil/tsil.h from pkginclude_HEADERS.

src/supermodel/tsil/tsil.h is listed both in src/supermodel/tsil.amk (the tsil
header group) and again in src/supermodel/supermodel.amk, so it ends up twice in
pkginclude_HEADERS. GNU coreutils `install` refuses to overwrite a file it just
created in the same invocation, so `make install` fails with:

    install: will not overwrite just-created '.../include/softsusy/tsil.h'

The build regenerates the autotools files with `autoreconf`, so the fix is made
in the Makefile.am fragment src/supermodel/supermodel.amk; the generated
Makefile.in is rebuilt from it.

diff --git a/src/supermodel/supermodel.amk b/src/supermodel/supermodel.amk
index ee8de54..0e3dcbf 100755
--- a/src/supermodel/supermodel.amk
+++ b/src/supermodel/supermodel.amk
@@ -36,5 +36,4 @@ src/supermodel/supermodel/sumo_params.h \
 src/supermodel/supermodel/sumo_smdata.h \
 src/supermodel/supermodel/sumo_squarks.h \
 src/supermodel/supermodel/supermodel_defs.h \
-src/supermodel/supermodel/supermodel.h \
-src/supermodel/tsil/tsil.h 
+src/supermodel/supermodel/supermodel.h
